          {
            "title": "Lesson #1",
            "id": 131820,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Vamos a explorar el uso de <code>continue</code>, <code>break</code> y <code>else</code> para controlar el flujo del bucle, omitir iteraciones, salir temprano o ejecutar código después del bucle.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2 - Copy",
            "id": 131844,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>continue</code> se utiliza para saltar el bloque actual y pasar a la siguiente iteración.</p><p>Asegúrate de no imprimir el número <code>2</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&gt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>==</code> seguido de <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 131821,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usa <code>continue</code> para saltar elementos específicos, como <code>\"chips\"</code> en un bucle, y pasar a la siguiente iteración.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shopping_list = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;apples&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;bananas&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;bread&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;milk&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;chips&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;eggs&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" item \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" shopping_list:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" item == \" /><text value=\"&quot;chips&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Don't forget to buy: \" /><text value=\"{item}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"126\" endIndex=\"134\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: apples\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: bananas\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: bread\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: milk\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: eggs\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 131845,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>La declaración <code>break</code> sale del bucle por completo. Si se invoca, no ejecuta el resto de las iteraciones.</p><p>Vamos a añadir una declaración <code>break</code> al programa para detener el bucle cuando <code>i</code> se convierta en <code>3</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>==</code> seguido de <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 131823,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos usar la palabra clave <code>break</code> para salir de un bucle <code>while</code> si se cumple una cierta condición, como una contraseña coincidente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"password = \" /><text value=\"&quot;open_sesame&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" input(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Enter the password: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") == password:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Access granted!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Incorrect password. Try again.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"119\" endIndex=\"124\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Incorrect password. Try again.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Incorrect password. Try again.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Access granted!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 131825,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Finalmente, la declaración <code>else</code> en los bucles se ejecuta cuando el bucle ha terminado. Recuerda, <code>else</code> en un bucle difiere de <code>else</code> en una declaración <code>if</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"'Loop has ended'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"37\" /><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loop has ended\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>else</code> seguido de <code>:</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 131826,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>El bloque <code>else</code> solo se ejecutará si el bucle no se termina antes de tiempo con una declaración <code>break</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"11\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loop has ended.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"62\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>break</code> seguido de <code>else:</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 131868,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifica la palabra clave que falta para imprimir una declaración final después de que el bucle haya pasado por todos los elementos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shows = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;The Office&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Dexter&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Friends&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" show \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" shows:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(show)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Those are my favorite shows!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"78\" endIndex=\"82\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"break\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"continue\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"The Office\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Dexter\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Friends\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Those are my favorite shows!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>else</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
